        "\"\"\"\n",
        "9.30.25\n",
        "<percentageFixedKeyRE>:\n",
        "- If Position_Copying_Enabled == True,\n",
        "-- Then <percentageFixedKeyRE> specifies the proportion of the key relative positions (histograms) that are\n",
        "**absolute** token positions, and not learnable, and the number that are learnable corresponding to (1-percentageFixedKeyRE)\n",
        "\"\"\"\n",
        "if Position_Copying_Enabled and not TRAIN_BASELINE_TRANSFORMER:\n",
